metadata.recording_metadata_summary: This recording is from a middle-school participating in the PLUS tutoring program. This school is called MACS. Students in this school use Chromebooks to access Zoom and generally use the math software IXL. The teacher in the classroom is named Mattes, although other teachers may be present. The tutor assigned to this classroom is named Jai Dalvi, although other tutors may be present.
